snippet.title: SNES Jaki Crush
snippet.description:
Support Shiryu on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/Shiryu
https://www.facebook.com/ShiryuVideoGames/

Often forgotten because it was only released in Japan, the third game of Compile's "Crush Pinball series was the Super Famicom Exclusive "Jaki Crush" and it brings to the the console all the same delights that PC Engine and Megadrive users were getting with the previous games. It could very well be the finest video pinball game on the system, if not for "Batlte Pinball". Enjoy!
